  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "synopsis",
      "abstract": "This Act removes the requirement that the counties each establish a Farmland Preservation Advisory Board.  This Act also makes technical corrections to conform existing law to the standards of the Delaware Legislative Drafting Manual."
